Rating: 4
This is one of my favorite salad dressings and I get rave reviews everytime I make it. One thing I use that really thickens the dressing is an Aerolatte instead of hand whisking, you will get great results if you use a frother like the Aerolatte when pouring the vegitable oil into the dressing. One other note: DON'T USE OLIVE OIL - it ruins the taste

