Rating: 4
A great dressing. To make it low fat, I used only 1 tablespoon of oil and added 1 tablespoon of white wine. You don't really need the wine - it just turned out slightly thicker than I wanted, so I diluted it a little with wine rather than oil. This dressing has a really round, well-balanced taste.

